  fhir:description [ fhir:v "IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.IPV-only\nInactivated polio vaccine (IPV)-only (in countries, in polio-free regions, with a very low risk of importation and sustained high routine immunization coverage (third dose of the diphtheria–tetanus–pertussis vaccine [DTP3] > 90%)"] ; # 
